aVQuantum mechanics was developed in the 1920s.
p59
aVIt is a set of beautiful and powerful mathematical rules and ideas
p60
aVthat explain the world of the very small.
p61
aVAnd it's a world that's very different from our everyday world,
p62
aVmade up of trillions of atoms.
p63
aVIt's a world built on probability and chance.
p64
aVIt's a fuzzy world.
p65
aVIt's a world of phantoms,
p66
aVwhere particles can also behave like spread-out waves.
