aa(lp127
VWell, one man begged to differ with this idea.
p128
aVErwin Schrödinger, of Schrödinger's Cat fame,
p129
aVwas an Austrian physicist.
p130
aVHe was one of the founders of quantum mechanics in the 1920s.
p131
aVIn 1944, he wrote a book called "What is Life?"
