aa(lp141
VIn fact, living matter seems to behave in this order, in a structure,
p142
aVjust like inanimate matter cooled down to near absolute zero,
p143
aVwhere quantum effects play a very important role.
p144
aVThere's something special about the structure \u2014 the order \u2014
p145
aVinside a living cell.
p146
aVSo, Schrödinger speculated that maybe quantum mechanics plays a role in life.
