p266
aVit follows multiple pathways at once,
p267
aVto optimize the most efficient way of reaching the reaction center
p268
aVwithout dissipating as waste heat.
p269
aVQuantum coherence taking place inside a living cell.
p270
aVA remarkable idea,
p271
aVand yet evidence is growing almost weekly, with new papers coming out,
